Vaibhav,

In the interrupt handler, it is better to add something like below... The
same piece of code is repeated many times... 

When ready to return IRQ_HANDLED

goto clear_int;


clear_int:
	if (vpfe_dev->cfg->clr_intr)
			vpfe_dev->cfg->clr_intr(irq);
	return IRQ_HANDLED;

